+#
+#         Win                     Lin
+# ---------------------------------------
+# Rax    Return           V       Return          V
+# Rbx                     NV                      NV
+# Rcx     Arg1            V       Arg4            V
+# Rdx     Arg2            V       Arg3            V
+# Rsi                     NV      Arg2            V
